    },
    {
      "term": "entropy_of_the_source",
      "gloss": "how much surprise, on average: the mind's own measure — expected surprise of the source, maximal when the symbols are equiprobable, zero when the receiver can already reproduce everything. the walls hold the census the measure would average over — counting licensed by permutation (Foam.freq, Foam.the_first_handshake_is_counting) and mass read at a seat (Foam.the_mass_is_a_reading) — and now the counting floor of coding (distinct_messages_need_distinct_marks), so the raw counts and the zeroth converse are already frontstage; expectation and the logarithm are not, and the theorems that price the floor exactly — the coding rates — are further still. the terminus, dark.",
